==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
Apparent neuter of a superlative from the same as [[ἄῤῥην]] {{GG|730}}; 

===Pronunciation===
*ἀριστον / ariston / ar'-is-ton

===Noun===
'''ἀριστον'''

# the best meal [or breakfast; perhaps from [[ἦρι]] ēri (“early”)], that is, [[luncheon]]: - [[dinner]].

